    "Ablation Studies (RQ3, RQ4)We conduct ablation studies to analyze the contribution of the three main modules of MPA: (i) counterfactual dataset generation, (ii) policy adapter, and (iii) Q-value guidance.Counterfactual Dataset.",
    "We further analyze the impact of the curated counterfactual dataset by ablating the step size during the rollout of counterfactual data.",
    "Then we train the MPA over the curated dataset and evaluate its performance in the unseen scenes in Boston, similar to the setting in Table 6 (left).",
    "We illustrate the trends of evaluation metrics with respect to the step sizes in the counterfactual dataset in Figure 6.",
    "MPA benefits from longer counterfactual steps, as there would be more informative supervision for the value function training in the future steps.Policy Adapter."
